The Map is about a littel Town where the only escape was a tunnel but its broken 
and instead of escaping you fight against them now!
The Humans got an littel advantage because they know the city ;P!
Well that map is specialsed for:

-Teamplay
-Hunt the Zombies
-Barricading
-Or just camp on a Box

So all what you need the fight or die!

Have fun with the Map

-Added 50 Spawns so more Players can play one the map now.
